data.description: Within a gated community, this charming one-story residence embodies modern sophistication both inside and out. Situated on a generous .25-acre lot, this cozy 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom home is the perfect retreat you've been searching for. As you approach this modern gem, you'll be immediately struck by its sleek and contemporary exterior. Its clean lines, thoughtfully designed landscaping, and welcoming curb appeal set the tone for the stylish interiors that await. Step through the front door, and you'll find yourself in a living space that seamlessly blends modern aesthetics with a cozy atmosphere. The two well-appointed bedrooms offer peaceful retreats while the shared bathroom exudes contemporary charm with its tasteful design and functional layout. While the interior of the home is undoubtedly captivating, the real magic awaits in the outdoor spaces. Your .25-acre lot provides ample room for gardening, outdoor dining, and creating your own private haven. Imagine sipping your morning coffee on the patio while soaking in the serene surroundings. Living in this secure gated community offers a sense of safety and peace of mind that is truly priceless. With a dedicated guard, you can rest easy knowing that your tranquility and privacy are paramount. Schedule your showing today!
